Whereas many people in Mzansi are complaining about the New Year, this young mlungu is different. He broke into the New Year with some sweet dance moves! A video which has been circulating on social media proves that dancing is a universal language. This young man is shown on the video performing difficult dance moves like the Thuso Phala with ease. While it is not clear where the video was taken, what was clear was that Twitter loved his moves. 